渡しを担う、<br data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>\n                すべての医療従事者のパートナーです。\n              </h3>\n              <p data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>\n                ムトウグループは創業以来100余年、全国屈指の販売拠点網、物流網を誇り、SPD運営を始め、医療・ウェルネス・理化学分野におけるあらゆる総合サービスを提供しています。<br data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>\n                更なる高みをめざし、信頼と品質向上に努め、全ての「いのち」と「健康」に向き合います。\n              </p>\n    \n              <div class=\"top__button\" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>\n                <a class=\"default-button\" href=\"/recruit_plus/about-us/#philosophy\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>\n  <p class=\"default-button__text\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>経営理念</p>\n  <div class=\"default-button__arrow\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7></div>\n</a>\n                <a class=\"default-button\" href=\"/recruit_plus/about-us/#whats\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>\n  <p class=\"default-button__text\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>ムトウとは</p>\n  <div class=\"default-button__arrow\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7></div>\n</a>\n                <a class=\"default-button\" href=\"/recruit_plus/about-us/#top-message\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>\n  <p class=\"default-button__text\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>代表ご挨拶</p>\n  <div class=\"default-button__arrow\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7></div>\n</a>\n                <a class=\"default-button\" href=\"/recruit_plus/about-us/#our-strengths\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>\n  <p class=\"default-button__text\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>ムトウの強み</p>\n  <div class=\"default-button__arrow\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7></div>\n</a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"top-about-us-slider\" class=\"top-about-us__slider swiper\" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>\n      <figure class=\"swiper-wrapper\" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>\n        <img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/main_slide01.jpg\" class=\"swiper-slide\" alt=\"\" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6><img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/main_slide02.jpg\" class=\"swiper-slide\" alt=\"\" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6><img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/i